divs: Sighting DetailsI wrote a detailed report but it was lost when I tried to submit. I cant type that much again. Moved in from east(lehigh acres), moved toward naples, than back towards its original path, then to west, then blinded by camera screen. Moved inhumanly fast and its movement was defined. Clean cut fast movement.
Summary: Fast moving object came in from east, made, triangular sweep pattern, lost object when blinded by phones camera display screen.
